                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>100000</citedRange></bibl>;
                <bibl><ptr target="#rosamilia2023"/>, pp. <citedRange>354-355</citedRange>, number 77 (text).</bibl></p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
